      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "PID cells: dynamic PhysicsBody + PhysicsLinearPID/AngularPID toward a Target (orbiting red ball) \u2014 Seek/Arrive, Pursue, Offset Pursuit, Evade, Look-At. GRID cells: transform agents on a named influence field \u2014 Flee (descend Threat), Seek (ascend an Objective mound), Separation (4 agents each stamp + descend the shared field). Reuses existing Threat/Objective fields. Not shown (need a query->force bridge / velocity field): predictive Pursue, Velocity Match."
